            <h3>Our History</h3>
            <p>HOW WE'VE STARTED OUR RESTAURANT</p>
          </div>
          <div id="history-description" class="col-md-8">
            <p>
              Ananya, our founder, spent several years working in a butcher shop
              in Brazil, where he learnt the significance of high-quality cuts.
              Our beef is ground in-house, resulting in high-quality burger
              patties that we are happy to serve to our visitors and our own
              family. Bernardo, A's culinary director, and Pillar, our Creative
              Director, both influenced our burger creations! Our burgers are
              all "smash burgers" and served medium-rare. Ananya'S delicious
              southern-style fried chicken sandwiches are cooked in our house
              buttermilk marinade, then breaded and crispy fried to order, for a
              crazy excellent crunch in every bite.
            </p>
          </div>
