                      <li>
                        Prepare food items according to recipe to ensure quality
                        and consistency of the final product
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Ensure that all prepared items are labeled, dated,
                        covered, and rotated
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Monitor food levels and replenish items in a timely
